charizard.name: charizard
charizard.entry_text: It spits fire that is hot enough to meltboulders. It may cause forest fires byblowing flames.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

tapu-koko.name: tapu-koko
tapu-koko.entry_text: This guardian deity of Melemele is brimming withcuriosity. It summons thunderclouds and storestheir lightning inside its body.  ~ Pokemon SUN

squirtle.name: squirtle
squirtle.entry_text: Shoots water at prey while in the water.Withdraws into its shell when in danger.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

deoxys-normal.name: deoxys-normal
deoxys-normal.entry_text: DEOXYS emerged from a virus that camefrom space. It is highly intelligent andwields psychokinetic powers. This POKéMON shoots lasers from thecrystalline organ on its chest.  ~ Pokemon SAPPHIRE

ho-oh.name: ho-oh
ho-oh.entry_text: Its feathers are in seven colors.It is said that anyone seeing it ispromised eternal happiness.  ~ Pokemon WHITE-2

mewtwo.name: mewtwo
mewtwo.entry_text: Its DNA is almost the same as Mew’s. However,its size and disposition are vastly different.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

mew.name: mew
mew.entry_text: Because it can use all kinds of moves, manyscientists believe Mew to be the ancestorof Pokémon.  ~ Pokemon X

bulbasaur.name: bulbasaur
bulbasaur.entry_text: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth.The plant sprouts and grows with this Pokémon.  ~ Pokemon X

ivysaur.name: ivysaur
ivysaur.entry_text: The bud on its back grows by drawing energy. Itgives off an aroma when it is ready to bloom.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

venusaur.name: venusaur
venusaur.entry_text: After a rainy day, the flower onits back smells stronger. Thescent attracts other Pokémon.  ~ Pokemon BLACK-2

charmander.name: charmander
charmander.entry_text: From the time it is born, a flame burns at the tipof its tail. Its life would end if the flame were togo out.  ~ Pokemon SHIELD

charmeleon.name: charmeleon
charmeleon.entry_text: Tough fights couldexcite thisPOKéMON. When excited, it mayblow out bluish-white flames.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

wartortle.name: wartortle
wartortle.entry_text: It cleverly controls its furryears and tail to maintain itsbalance while swimming.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

blastoise.name: blastoise
blastoise.entry_text: The rocket cannons on its shell firejets of water capable of punchingholes through thick steel.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

caterpie.name: caterpie
caterpie.entry_text: Its short feetare tipped withsuction pads that enable it totirelessly climbslopes and walls.  ~ Pokemon RED

metapod.name: metapod
metapod.entry_text: Hardens its shellto protect itself.However, a large impact may causeit to pop out ofits shell.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

butterfree.name: butterfree
butterfree.entry_text: Water-repellentpowder on itswings enables it to collect honey,even in the heav­iest of rains.  ~ Pokemon SILVER

weedle.name: weedle
weedle.entry_text: It eats its weight in leaves everyday. It fends off attackers withthe needle on its head.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

kakuna.name: kakuna
kakuna.entry_text: While awaiting evolution, ithides from predators underleaves and in nooks of branches.  ~ Pokemon WHITE-2

beedrill.name: beedrill
beedrill.entry_text: It has 3 poisonousstingers on itsforelegs and its tail. They areused to jab itsenemy repeatedly.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

pidgey.name: pidgey
pidgey.entry_text: It is docile and prefers to avoidconflict. If disturbed, however,it can ferociously strike back.  ~ Pokemon WHITE

pidgeotto.name: pidgeotto
pidgeotto.entry_text: It flies over its wide territory insearch of prey, downing itwith its highly developed claws.  ~ Pokemon PLATINUM

pidgeot.name: pidgeot
pidgeot.entry_text: By flapping its wings with all itsmight, Pidgeot can make a gust ofwind capable of bending tall trees.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

rattata.name: rattata
rattata.entry_text: Its incisors grow continuously throughout its life.If its incisors get too long, this Pokémonbecomes unable to eat, and it starves to death.  ~ Pokemon ULTRA-SUN

raticate.name: raticate
raticate.entry_text: It whittles its constantly growingfangs by gnawing on hard things.It can chew apart cinder walls.  ~ Pokemon DIAMOND

spearow.name: spearow
spearow.entry_text: It flaps its small wings busily tofly. Using its beak, it searchesin grass for prey.  ~ Pokemon BLACK-2

fearow.name: fearow
fearow.entry_text: With its huge andmagnificent wings,it can keep aloft without everhaving to landfor rest.  ~ Pokemon BLUE

ekans.name: ekans
ekans.entry_text: Ekans curls itself up in a spiral while it rests. Assuming thisposition allows it to quickly respond to a threat from anydirection with a glare from its upraised head.  ~ Pokemon ALPHA-SAPPHIRE

arbok.name: arbok
arbok.entry_text: It is rumored that the ferocious warningmarkings on its belly differ from area toarea.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

pikachu.name: pikachu
pikachu.entry_text: It occasionally uses an electricshock to recharge a fellow Pikachuthat is in a weakened state.  ~ Pokemon WHITE

raichu.name: raichu
raichu.entry_text: It loves pancakes prepared with a secret Alolanrecipe. Some wonder whether that recipe holdsthe key to this Pokémon’s evolution.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

sandshrew.name: sandshrew
sandshrew.entry_text: Its ice-covered body lets it slide across theground with bullet-like speed, sending itsenemies flying when it hits them.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

sandslash.name: sandslash
sandslash.entry_text: It curls up, then rolls into foeswith its back. Its sharp spinesinflict severe damage.  ~ Pokemon WHITE

nidoran-f.name: nidoran-f
nidoran-f.entry_text: A mild-mannered Pokémon that does not liketo fight. Beware—its small horn secretes venom.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

salamence.name: salamence
salamence.entry_text: It flies around on its wings, which have grown inat last. In its happiness, it gushes hot flames,burning up the fields it passes over.  ~ Pokemon MOON

beldum.name: beldum
beldum.entry_text: It uses magnetic waves to converse withits kind. All the cells in its body aremagnetic.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED

metang.name: metang
metang.entry_text: When two BELDUM fuse together, METANGis formed. The brains of the BELDUM arejoined by a magnetic nervous system. By linking its brains magnetically,this POKéMON generates strongpsychokinetic power.  ~ Pokemon RUBY

metagross.name: metagross
metagross.entry_text: Metang combined to form it.With four brains, it has theintelligence of a supercomputer.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

regirock.name: regirock
regirock.entry_text: Regirock’s body is composed entirely of rocks. Recently,a study made the startling discovery that the rocks were allunearthed from different locations.  ~ Pokemon ALPHA-SAPPHIRE

lugia.name: lugia
lugia.entry_text: It sleeps in a deep-sea trench.If it flaps its wings, it is said tocause a 40-day storm.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

nidoran\u2640.name: nidoran♀
nidoran\u2640.entry_text: NIDORAN has barbs that secrete apowerful poison. They are thought tohave developed as protection for this small-bodied POKéMON.When enraged, it releases a horribletoxin from its horn.  ~ Pokemon SAPPHIRE

nidorina.name: nidorina
nidorina.entry_text: When resting deep in its burrow, its barbs alwaysretract. This is proof that it is relaxed.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

nidoran\u2642.name: nidoran♂
nidoran\u2642.entry_text: It constantlymoves its largeears in many directions inorder to detectdanger right away.  ~ Pokemon CRYSTAL

nidoqueen.name: nidoqueen
nidoqueen.entry_text: Its entire body is armored withhard scales. It will protect theyoung in its burrow with its life.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

nidorino.name: nidorino
nidorino.entry_text: Its horns containvenom. If theyare stabbed into an enemy, theimpact makes thepoison leak out.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

nidoking.name: nidoking
nidoking.entry_text: Its steel-like hide adds to its powerful tackle.Its horns are so hard, they can pierce a diamond.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

clefairy.name: clefairy
clefairy.entry_text: With its magical and cute appeal, it has many admirers. It is rare and found onlyin certain areas.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

clefable.name: clefable
clefable.entry_text: CLEFABLE moves by skipping lightly as ifit were flying using its wings. Itsbouncy step lets it even walk on water. It is known to take strolls on lakes onquiet, moonlit nights.  ~ Pokemon RUBY

vulpix.name: vulpix
vulpix.entry_text: Inside Vulpix’s body burns a flame that never goes out.During the daytime, when the temperatures rise, thisPokémon releases flames from its mouth to prevent itsbody from growing too hot.  ~ Pokemon ALPHA-SAPPHIRE

ninetales.name: ninetales
ninetales.entry_text: It lives on mountains perpetually covered insnow and is revered as a deity incarnate.It appears draped in a blizzard.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

jigglypuff.name: jigglypuff
jigglypuff.entry_text: When its huge eyeslight up, it singsa mysteriously soothing melodythat lulls itsenemies to sleep.  ~ Pokemon BLUE

wigglytuff.name: wigglytuff
wigglytuff.entry_text: Its fine fur feels sublime to thetouch. It can expand its body byinhaling air.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

zubat.name: zubat
zubat.entry_text: Capable of flyingsafely in darkplaces, it emits ultrasonic criesto check for anyobstacles.  ~ Pokemon SILVER

golbat.name: golbat
golbat.entry_text: It attacks in a stealthy manner,without warning. Its sharp fangsare used to bite and to suck blood.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

oddish.name: oddish
oddish.entry_text: ODDISH searches for fertile, nutrient-rich soil, then plants itself.During the daytime, while it is planted, this POKéMON’s feet are thought tochange shape and become similar tothe roots of trees.  ~ Pokemon SAPPHIRE

gloom.name: gloom
gloom.entry_text: A horribly noxious honey drools from itsmouth. One whiff of the honey can resultin memory loss. Some fans are said toenjoy this overwhelming stink, however.  ~ Pokemon EMERALD

vileplume.name: vileplume
vileplume.entry_text: The bud burstsinto bloom with abang. It then starts scatteringallergenic, poi­sonous pollen.  ~ Pokemon SILVER

paras.name: paras
paras.entry_text: Mushrooms called tochukaso sprout from itsback. They can be dried and powdered to makea medicine used to extend life.  ~ Pokemon MOON

parasect.name: parasect
parasect.entry_text: It scatters toxic spores from its mushroom cap.Once harvested, these spores can be steepedand boiled down to prepare herbal medicines.  ~ Pokemon MOON

venonat.name: venonat
venonat.entry_text: Its big eyes are actually clustersof tiny eyes. At night, its kind isdrawn by light.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

venomoth.name: venomoth
venomoth.entry_text: VENOMOTH is nocturnal - it is a POKéMONthat only becomes active at night.Its favorite prey are small insects that gather around streetlights,attracted by the light in the darkness.  ~ Pokemon SAPPHIRE

diglett.name: diglett
diglett.entry_text: A Pokémon that lives underground.Because of its dark habitat, it isrepelled by bright sunlight.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

dugtrio.name: dugtrio
dugtrio.entry_text: In battle, it digs through the ground andstrikes the unsuspecting foe from anunexpected direction.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED

meowth.name: meowth
meowth.entry_text: It is fascinated by round objects.It can’t stop playing with themuntil it tires and falls asleep.  ~ Pokemon HEARTGOLD

persian.name: persian
persian.entry_text: Although its fur has many admirers, it is toughto raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.  ~ Pokemon X

psyduck.name: psyduck
psyduck.entry_text: While lulling itsenemies with itsvacant look, this wily POKéMON willuse psychokineticpowers.  ~ Pokemon BLUE

golduck.name: golduck
golduck.entry_text: Often seen swim­ming elegantly bylake shores. It is often mistakenfor the Japanesemonster, Kappa.  ~ Pokemon BLUE

mankey.name: mankey
mankey.entry_text: Light and agile on its feet, and ferociousin temperament. When angered, it flies intoan uncontrollable frenzy.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED

primeape.name: primeape
primeape.entry_text: It has been known to become so angry thatit dies as a result. Its face looks peaceful indeath, however.  ~ Pokemon SUN

growlithe.name: growlithe
growlithe.entry_text: Very friendly and faithful to people. It will try torepel enemies by barking and biting.  ~ Pokemon X

arcanine.name: arcanine
arcanine.entry_text: Its proud and regal appearancehas captured the hearts ofpeople since long ago.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

poliwag.name: poliwag
poliwag.entry_text: Its skin is so thin, its internalorgans are visible. It has troublewalking on its newly grown feet.  ~ Pokemon PLATINUM

poliwhirl.name: poliwhirl
poliwhirl.entry_text: The spiral pattern on its bellysubtly undulates. Staring at itgradually causes drowsiness.  ~ Pokemon BLACK

poliwrath.name: poliwrath
poliwrath.entry_text: With its extremely tough muscles,it can keep swimming in the PacificOcean without resting.  ~ Pokemon WHITE

abra.name: abra
abra.entry_text: If it decides to teleport randomly,it evokes the illusion that ithas created copies of itself.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

kadabra.name: kadabra
kadabra.entry_text: If one is nearby, an eerie shadowappears on TV screens. Seeing theshadow is said to bring bad luck.  ~ Pokemon DIAMOND

alakazam.name: alakazam
alakazam.entry_text: It has an incredibly high level of intelligence.Some say that Alakazam remembers everythingthat ever happens to it, from birth till death.  ~ Pokemon SWORD

machop.name: machop
machop.entry_text: It continually undertakes strenuoustraining to master all forms of martialarts. Its strength lets it easily hoista sumo wrestler onto its shoulders.  ~ Pokemon EMERALD

machoke.name: machoke
machoke.entry_text: MACHOKE undertakes bodybuilding everyday even as it helps people with tough,physically demanding labor. On its days off, this POKéMON heads tothe fields and mountains to exerciseand train.  ~ Pokemon SAPPHIRE

machamp.name: machamp
machamp.entry_text: Its superpowerful punches are said toknock the victim flying clear over thehorizon.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

bellsprout.name: bellsprout
bellsprout.entry_text: It prefers hot and humidenvironments. It is quick atcapturing prey with its vines.  ~ Pokemon DIAMOND

weepinbell.name: weepinbell
weepinbell.entry_text: A Pokémon that appears to be aplant. It captures unwary prey bydousing them with a toxic powder.  ~ Pokemon DIAMOND

victreebel.name: victreebel
victreebel.entry_text: Said to live in huge colonies deep injungles, although no one has everreturned from there.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

tentacool.name: tentacool
tentacool.entry_text: Drifts in shallow seas. Anglers who hookthem by accident are often punished bytheir stingers.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

tentacruel.name: tentacruel
tentacruel.entry_text: Its 80 tentaclescan stretch andcontract freely. They wrap aroundprey and weakenit with poison.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

geodude.name: geodude
geodude.entry_text: The longer a GEODUDE lives, the moreits edges are chipped and worn away,making it more rounded in appearance. However, this POKéMON’s heart willremain hard, craggy, and rough always.  ~ Pokemon RUBY

graveler.name: graveler
graveler.entry_text: Mossy rocks are its favorite food.It can devour a ton a day while crunching loudly.  ~ Pokemon SUN

golem.name: golem
golem.entry_text: It is said to live in volcanic craterson mountain peaks. Once a year, it shedsits hide and grows larger. The shed hidecrumbles and returns to the soil.  ~ Pokemon EMERALD

ponyta.name: ponyta
ponyta.entry_text: Its hind legs, which have hooves thatare harder than diamond, kick backat any presence it senses behind it.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

rapidash.name: rapidash
rapidash.entry_text: It usually canters casually in the fieldsand plains. But once a RAPIDASH turnsserious, its fiery manes flare and blazeas it gallops its way up to 150 mph.  ~ Pokemon EMERALD

slowpoke.name: slowpoke
slowpoke.entry_text: Because Galarian Slowpoke eat the seeds of aplant that grows only in Galar, their tails havedeveloped a spicy flavor.  ~ Pokemon SHIELD

slowbro.name: slowbro
slowbro.entry_text: Though usually dim witted, itseems to become inspired if theSHELLDER on its tail bites down.  ~ Pokemon PLATINUM

magnemite.name: magnemite
magnemite.entry_text: The faster the units at its sidesrotate, the greater the magneticforce they generate.  ~ Pokemon PLATINUM

magneton.name: magneton
magneton.entry_text: It is actually three MAGNEMITElinked by magnetism. A group canset off a magnetic storm.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

farfetchd.name: farfetchd
farfetchd.entry_text: It always walks about with a plant stalkclamped in its beak. The stalk is used forbuilding its nest.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED

doduo.name: doduo
doduo.entry_text: The brains in its two heads appearto communicate emotions to eachother with a telepathic power.  ~ Pokemon BLACK-2

dodrio.name: dodrio
dodrio.entry_text: An odd species that is rarely found.The three heads respectively representjoy, sadness, and anger.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED

seel.name: seel
seel.entry_text: The protruding horn on its head is veryhard. It is used for bashing through thickicebergs.  ~ Pokemon LEAFGREEN

dewgong.name: dewgong
dewgong.entry_text: In snow, the pure white coatcovering its body obscures it frompredators.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

grimer.name: grimer
grimer.entry_text: Made of congealed sludge. It smells too putridto touch. Even weeds won’t grow in its path.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

muk.name: muk
muk.entry_text: Its body is made of a powerful poison.Touching it accidentally willcause a fever that requires bed rest.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

shellder.name: shellder
shellder.entry_text: The shell canwithstand anyattack. However, when it is open,the tender bodyis exposed.  ~ Pokemon YELLOW

cloyster.name: cloyster
cloyster.entry_text: For protection, it uses its harder-than-diamondshell. It also shoots spikes from the shell.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

gastly.name: gastly
gastly.entry_text: Should a strange light be seen flickeringin an abandoned building, Gastly is lurking there.  ~ Pokemon SUN

haunter.name: haunter
haunter.entry_text: It likes to lurk in the dark and tapshoulders with a gaseous hand. Itstouch causes endless shuddering.  ~ Pokemon WHITE-2

gengar.name: gengar
gengar.entry_text: A Gengar is close by if you feel a sudden chill.It may be trying to lay a curse on you.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

onix.name: onix
onix.entry_text: ONIX has a magnet in its brain. It actsas a compass so that this POKéMON doesnot lose direction while it is tunneling. As it grows older, its body becomesincreasingly rounder and smoother.  ~ Pokemon RUBY

drowzee.name: drowzee
drowzee.entry_text: If you think that you had a good dreambut you can’t remember it,a DROWZEE has probably eaten it.  ~ Pokemon HEARTGOLD

hypno.name: hypno
hypno.entry_text: Seeing its swinging pendulum caninduce sleep in three seconds,even in someone who just woke up.  ~ Pokemon PEARL

krabby.name: krabby
krabby.entry_text: If it senses danger approaching, it cloaks itself withbubbles from its mouth so it will look bigger.  ~ Pokemon X

kingler.name: kingler
kingler.entry_text: Its large and hard pincer has 10,000-horsepowerstrength. However, being so big, it is unwieldyto move.  ~ Pokemon SWORD

voltorb.name: voltorb
voltorb.entry_text: It looks just like a Poké Ball.It is dangerous because it mayelectrocute or explode on contact.  ~ Pokemon WHITE-2

electrode.name: electrode
electrode.entry_text: It stores an overflowing amount of electric energyinside its body. Even a small shock makesit explode.  ~ Pokemon Y

exeggcute.name: exeggcute
exeggcute.entry_text: The heads attract each other and spinaround. There must be six heads for it tomaintain balance.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-PIKACHU

exeggutor.name: exeggutor
exeggutor.entry_text: If a head drops off, it emits atelepathic call in search of othersto form an EXEGGCUTE cluster.  ~ Pokemon SOULSILVER

cubone.name: cubone
cubone.entry_text: When it thinks of its dead mother,it cries. Its crying makes theskull it wears rattle hollowly.  ~ Pokemon DIAMOND

marowak.name: marowak
marowak.entry_text: Originally, it was weak and timid. After evolution,its temperament becomes violent, and it beginsto wield bones as weapons.  ~ Pokemon SUN

hitmonlee.name: hitmonlee
hitmonlee.entry_text: When kicking, the sole of its foot turns as hardas a diamond on impact and destroys its enemy.  ~ Pokemon LETS-GO-EEVEE

hitmonchan.name: hitmonchan
hitmonchan.entry_text: The spirit of a pro boxer has infused thisPOKéMON. It throws punches that arefaster than a bullet train.  ~ Pokemon FIRERED
